Text: "I\u2019m an Argentinian based photographer, traveling the world having the\
  \ opportunity to get to known other cultures that aren\u2019t beyond ours, that\u2019\
  s how I discovered Japan, in the other side of the world, where the day is night\
  \ , and night is day, and my goal was to deeply connect with the culture, to feel\
  \ their daily and their past, and how, in a remote country far from Argentina, there\u2019\
  s another humans living life completely different"
